sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as trustyai-service-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JobPod as lmes-job Pod<br/>(main.py)
    participant ConfigMap as ConfigMap<br/>/meta/job.json
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>Configurable Port HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>Configurable HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 1: EvalHub Job Execution
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job from LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.3
        K8sAPI-->>JobPod: Pod scheduled & started

        JobPod->>ConfigMap: Read job spec<br/>(filesystem mount)
        Note over JobPod: Parse JobSpec JSON:<br/>model, benchmark_id, params

        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
        EvalHub-->>JobPod: 200 OK

        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        JobPod->>HFHub: GET benchmark datasets<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HFHub-->>JobPod: Dataset artifacts

        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

        loop For each evaluation prompt (up to 128 concurrent)
            JobPod->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA supported)
            Model-->>JobPod: Completion response
        end

        Note over JobPod: Compute metrics<br/>(117 metric types)

        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

        JobPod->>OCI: Push result artifacts<br/>Auth: Registry Auth<br/>TLS 1.2+
        OCI-->>JobPod: Push confirmed

        JobPod->>MLflow: Log metrics & run metadata<br/>Auth: Configurable<br/>TLS 1.2+
        MLflow-->>JobPod: run_id

        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>+ evaluation results<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        EvalHub-->>JobPod: 200 OK
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over JobPod,Model: Flow 2: Offline/Disconnected Evaluation
        participant S3 as S3/COS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant InitC as Init Container
        participant Volume as /test_data Volume

        InitC->>S3: Download cached datasets<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / IBM COS<br/>TLS 1.2+
        S3-->>InitC: Dataset archives
        InitC->>Volume: Write to /test_data

        Note over JobPod: HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_EVALUATE_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1

        JobPod->>Volume: Read cached datasets<br/>(HF_HOME=/test_data)

        loop Evaluation prompts
            JobPod->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
            Model-->>JobPod: Completion response
        end
    end
